org.apache.commons.math4.linear

Class DefaultFieldMatrixPreservingVisitor<T extends FieldElement<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.math4.linear.DefaultFieldMatrixPreservingVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the field elements
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FieldMatrixPreservingVisitor<T>

    public class DefaultFieldMatrixPreservingVisitor<T extends FieldElement<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FieldMatrixPreservingVisitor<T>
    Default implementation of the FieldMatrixPreservingVisitor interface.

    This class is a convenience to create custom visitors without defining all methods. This class provides default implementations that do nothing.

    Since:
    2.0
